original_title: Shoot Conversations w/ Chris Hero: Molly Holly
overview: The #HSWN is excited to debut a brand new interview series, "Shoot Conversations w/ Chris Hero", and what an incredible guest for a debut show, Molly Holly! Chris sits down with one of the genuinely nicest people in professional wrestling and digs deep into her journey in the strange world of pro wrestling. Sit back and enjoy this "Shoot Conversation"!
title: Shoot Conversations w/ Chris Hero: Molly Holly
